                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Tracks in fresh snow. You were seen the moment you set foot on the pass. Nothing crosses Frostveil unmarked."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Nifl Town is past the drifts and Boreas holds the Ice gym there - patient as a glacier and twice as cold. Battle me first, or square the crossing."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I warden this pass so the unprepared do not feed the ice. Face me and prove your team can take the cold, or pay the crossing and go careful."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Frostwarden Neve",
                    Label: "default"
